Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.81,0:00:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.43,0:00:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still not fixed?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.92,0:00:21.25,Top,,0,0,0,,Even I can't work miracles, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.25,0:00:24.67,Top,,0,0,0,,You crashed it yesterday, brought it in, \Nand now you want it painted too? {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.67,0:00:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut me some slack! \NI've got a date with Miko-chan today.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.71,0:00:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been ages since I've had a chance \Nto score with an upstanding girl! {shirouto = respectable woman (i.e. not a prostitute, hostess, geisha)​}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.74,0:00:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe you should've taken it easy last night.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.77,0:00:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.81,0:00:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when do you talk back to me like that, huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.15,0:00:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm telling you, it's just not possible—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.82,0:00:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.80,0:00:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.66,0:00:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi, have one of your buddies \Nbring his car here.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.12,0:00:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? You can't take a girl out \Non a date in a bus, can you?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.40,0:01:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, I don't really have \Nany more friends to turn to.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.84,0:01:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.26,0:01:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I lend one of their rides to you, \NI lose face with my pals. {lit: lose friends}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.32,0:01:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one day of your "rolling," \Nand the whole suspension's wrecked! {korogashita}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.10,0:01:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they come to me for repair money.\NIt's killing me, boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.86,0:01:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fixing it is your damn job, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.53,0:01:33.70,Top,,0,0,0,,And if I rent a car, \NI won't have enough left for the hotel.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.28,0:01:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless underlings are more trouble \Nthan they're worth.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.76,0:01:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's too cold to do it outdoors anyway. {aokan = public sex}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.22,0:01:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! You're so selfish, Ryo-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.65,0:01:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.23,0:01:50.69,Top,,0,0,0,,I hate this kind of car! \NDon't you have a BMW?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.69,0:01:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on, don't say that!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.07,0:01:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the only thing I could get!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said I wanted to be picked up in a bus!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.82,0:02:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But hey, this bus is all yours, \NMiko-chan. A private ride!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.56,0:02:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.57,0:02:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only get in a Porsche or BMW! \NNo, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.14,0:02:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now... \NYou knew from the start I didn't have one!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.55,0:02:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so impossible, Miko-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.48,0:02:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess that's how it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.83,0:02:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a bus driver.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.04,0:02:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If she hates me, so be it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.43,0:02:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't blame her when I'm rolling around \Nin a hunk of junk like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.48,0:02:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps even a bus will do for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.36,0:02:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,These five years have turned me \Ninto a tougher man.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.63,0:02:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've returned to the town where Ryota lives.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.26,0:02:46.50,Narrtop,,0,0,0,,Fujioka Sanji, from Tomioka City, Gunma Prefecture.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.50,0:02:50.50,Narrtop,,0,0,0,,Former biker gang member. \NFamily business: making konjac jelly. {lit: making konnyakudama - there's no such thing as Konjac balls so idk what it means, maybe actually Konjac jelly which also seems to be that thing drawn on the side of his truck?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.17,0:02:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota, I'm not the same guy I was back then.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.78,0:03:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell are you, Ryota?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.04,0:03:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota, I swear I'll outrun you \Nand bring glory back to Tomioka. {this "okkaa" seems to be some meaningless interjection peculiar to him, maybe something like "all right..."; probably from gunma dialect}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.82,0:03:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where should we go, Miko-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.25,0:03:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's see... \NWhere's a good place?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.22,0:03:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Parking there like he owns the road!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.64,0:03:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell? Gunma? Konjac?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.06,0:03:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn hick farmer!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.74,0:03:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My beloved truck, \Nmore precious than my life!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.63,0:03:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Come back here, you idiot! \NMoron! Gas guzzler! {???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.84,0:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Who the hell are you calling \Na moron, you bumpkin bastard?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.93,0:03:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo... Ryo... Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.48,0:03:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.34,0:03:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Konjac Sanji himself!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Still kicking, huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.84,0:03:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Still making jelly blocks, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.09,0:03:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta say, that farmer look\N sure suits you, man!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.51,0:03:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.52,0:04:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that outfit, Miko-chan! \NHis family makes konjac jelly, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Awful!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.12,0:04:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's always been a boneless man! {literal - boneless like the jelly, and also idiomatically means "without a backbone/limp/coward"}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.84,0:04:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.15,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, Ryota. \NI'm not the same man anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.73,0:04:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been training in Usui Pass \Njust to beat you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeehaw!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and keep up, Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, the guy's not half bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.77,0:04:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you going to race him? \NYay! Go for it! Don't lose!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.26,0:04:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so exhilarating! {lit: I'm on fire}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it, sis! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's roll!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.01,0:04:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, I'm ahead of Ryota now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.86,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years ago, that was unthinkable.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.67,0:04:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, no matter how I tried, \NI couldn't stay ahead of him for ten seconds.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.46,0:04:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.46,0:05:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So what was all that revving up for!? {?? something like "what's wrong? didn't you challenge me"}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.41,0:05:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed a bit in five years, have you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.02,0:05:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,See that, Miko-chan? He's already eating dust.\N He's totally no match for me! {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.46,0:05:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! We're breaking away! \NCome on, faster, floor it! {??????? can't hear shit in the first half}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.67,0:05:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get hurt, all my plans \Nwill go down the drain! {??? I assume this onisan is ryota himself, then he's openly telling her "I wanted to bang you today, but not if you're a cripple"}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.00,0:05:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Plans?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.12,0:05:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ryota-san, I feel so good! \NDo it harder. I like it rough!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.34,0:05:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, if you got hurt, \Nthat'd be bad, right? Yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sniff you later! {osaki = I'm going ahead/first}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I passed him twice! Twice!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota's got nothing on me! {lit: is no opponent for me}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.26,0:05:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. Celebrating after\N overtaking a stopped bus...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What a simpleminded hick!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.10,0:05:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what plans? What plans?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.67,0:05:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.86,0:06:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take him down with the cornering technique \NI mastered in the Usui Pass!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.39,0:06:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.75,0:06:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The city curves are sharper than I thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.21,0:06:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-What the...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.03,0:06:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace! Konjac Sanji, what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.24,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap. I knew it. The guy's a genius.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.65,0:06:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping up in a bus \Nthat's a size bigger than my car... {aisha = beloved/favorite car}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.06,0:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. Guess I'll get knocked \Noff the course like always.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And that'll be the end of it again.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.43,0:06:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap... if I blow it here, my youth's finished. {lit: pitch black}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.35,0:06:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A railroad crossing. \NIf I time it right, I can lose Ryota here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.16,0:06:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... now!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.66,0:07:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my konjac! {????? maybe a wordplay where he combines "what the hell" with "konyaku"}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm finished!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That dumbass!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.82,0:07:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Looks like I was saved, somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.84,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, Ryota's the king \Nof rear-end collisions. {lit: okama thrusting - seems like some bosozoku slang for rear-ending, like in previous episode?}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.11,0:07:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck! Why'd it decide to get stuck standing up?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.95,0:07:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something else that was supposed \Nto stand up right now! {don't quite understand what he says but seems to be some joke to the extent of "we were about to go to the hotel where my willy needed to stand up, and now we're stuck in a bus standing up"... another one of those lines that make me question my life choices}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.54,0:07:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy even makes wrecks look spectacular. {lit: he's a man who makes everything a picture}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.85,0:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miko-chan! You okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.46,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, she fainted from the shock!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.40,0:08:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Ryota-san'll give you a big, \Nstrong shot to wake you up.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.85,0:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this warmth, this softness... Youth really is something else.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.19,0:08:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Ryota-san, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I naked?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.76,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, see, you fainted, so I figured I'd give you\Na special shot to wake you up nice and easy. {chuusha = injection}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? There's a shot like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.18,0:08:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.25,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do it! Quick, Ryota-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.68,0:08:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.78,0:08:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's already five o'clock?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.77,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a date with Michio-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A date? When I'm right here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.64,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, taxi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.27,0:09:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, Miko-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.49,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll breastfeed you some other time, okay? {0_0 wild but seems to be what she actually says}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, Ryota-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.41,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, the upstanding girl blueballed me, \Nand the only thing that stood tall was the bus. {???? I hear "indeed, cold one is the shiroto (honest woman) girl, and only bus stands"}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.08,0:09:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, thank you so much...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.80,0:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for you, Ryota-san, I'd be...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.19,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.59,0:09:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't shown up, I'd be in a motel,\N getting busy with her right now, dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.48,0:09:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Think with that dick-shaped head of yours\N and tell me what I'm supposed to do now! {lit: head like the glans (esp. glans penis)}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.98,0:09:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent a whole week \Ntuning that thing, you idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.40,0:09:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, about that...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use this.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.44,0:09:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Warm it up to body temperature, and once it's nice and warm, there's nothing better than this.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, I get hard three times a day.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.41,0:10:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You serious right now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.33,0:10:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean, serious as in...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.76,0:10:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You schmuck!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.82,0:10:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell do I have to deal with it\N by using a konjac jelly, huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.34,0:10:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But come on, everyone at Tomioka does it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.70,0:10:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lump me in with you losers, \Nyou turtlehead! {literal - unless it's some other word for penis, idk how he managed to compare that shape to a turtle}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.56,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah... When that time comes, \NI start feeling all tingly down there. {lit: my crotch itches}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.94,0:10:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a man's weapon hanging between our legs, and we're letting it go to waste.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.74,Top,,0,0,0,,Not like we've got money to buy a woman, though. {literal}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.74,0:10:40.66,Top,,0,0,0,,Would be nice to find a hot chick and get it on, right, Yoshimoto?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.81,0:10:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You freeze up stiff every time you see a girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.12,0:10:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? You're one to talk, man!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.59,0:10:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch! Guess that makes us even.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.91,0:10:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should go over to Takashi's place \Nand gawk at Yuki-chan's mini for a bit?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.57,0:10:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sounds good.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.25,0:11:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's wearing\N something real risky today.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.27,0:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Takashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.25,0:11:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's delivering a tire.\NHe's actually working for once, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.96,0:11:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tajima, you {\i1}do{\i0} realize that means Yuki-chan's alone in the shop right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.28,0:11:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we gotta hurry! \NLet's admire the view while no one's around. {to interrupt us}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.40,0:11:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.18,0:11:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this, Yuki-chan? \NYou're wearing some boring jeans.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.84,0:11:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your usual miniskirt?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.01,0:11:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mini? What, I'm not allowed\N to wear jeans now?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.46,0:11:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw man, no mini on Yuki-chan? \NIt cuts your charm in half.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.94,0:11:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We came running thinking Takashi wasn't here. What a downer.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.82,0:12:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta rock \Na mini year-round, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At least fifteen centimeters\N above the knee too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.12,0:12:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the queen of peeks and flashes, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.02,0:12:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wearing jeans that cover everything up? \NThat won't get me excited.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.81,0:12:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wear minis to get \Nyou guys excited, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.40,0:12:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Yoshimoto.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No point hanging around here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.30,0:12:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, a woman only gets prettier \Nwhen she's admired.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.81,0:12:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep dressing like that, and you'll get thigh fat lines soon enough. No one'll look at you twice.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.43,0:12:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,N-None of your business!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.16,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this, Yuki-chan? \NJeans today, huh? What a shame.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.74,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.91,0:12:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We told her we preferred the minis too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.57,0:12:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it's none of our business.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.67,0:12:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, jeans aren't bad, but still...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.52,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not Yuki-chan without those sexy thighs out in the open.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.24,0:13:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?\N I'll buy you a skirt. Super mini!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.63,0:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta treat Yuki-chan once in a while!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.25,0:13:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.17,0:13:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you one
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.65,0:13:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,just the way I like it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.53,0:13:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was pretty forward of him.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.44,0:13:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, do minis suit me that much?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.14,0:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Minis were made \Nfor girls like you, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.29,0:13:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When Ryota brings it, \Nlet us have a good look, yeah? Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.46,0:13:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If you strike a sexy pose and flash \Na bit of that panty, I'd even pay for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.14,0:13:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, money?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.77,0:13:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe. If you promise not to touch me, I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.58,0:13:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really? How much? \NHow much'll it take?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us a friend's discount, all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.75,0:14:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, some conceited broad \Nis running her mouth here as well?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.34,0:14:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.87,0:14:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.87,0:14:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...the hell are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.79,0:14:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wander the nation to punish women \Nwho've grown vain from being spoiled by men.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.19,0:14:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since men got softer, there's been \Nmore and more of you vain women every year.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.13,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Last summer alone, \NI punished them in dozens on the beach.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you rambling about?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.99,0:14:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you waddle back \Nto your sumo stable and eat some stew?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoo! Shoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.21,0:14:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.26,0:14:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Men I can forgive.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.68,0:14:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They say nice things just to get laid.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.92,0:14:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But the vain women who get drunk on those words, who bask in the attention...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Those women I can never forgive!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.11,0:14:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.52,0:14:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need some fat stranger lecturing me! {they all think it's a man btw}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.80,0:14:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fat?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.09,0:15:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You'd better leave now,\N before I get mad.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell, you douchebag?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.70,0:15:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 'cause your face is a bit pretty,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.19,0:15:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,your chest a bit perky,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.87,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and your waist a bit slim, \Ndon't get so full of yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.76,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure you never brag \Nabout that body again!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.18,0:15:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!{Sona}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only getting started! {????? something about "here's another one"}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you call that punishment?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.12,0:15:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're trying to do \Nis no different from assault!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.60,0:15:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can decide that after we're done.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.48,0:16:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.57,0:16:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, there were too many kinds. \NI couldn't choose.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.46,0:16:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up getting a leather mini.\N Hope you like it...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.26,0:16:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.75,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.09,0:16:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ow-ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.59,0:16:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.84,0:16:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a lot went down while I was gone, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.30,0:16:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Should've bought you a jacket too, at this rate.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.97,0:16:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not one of those disgusting guys, spoiling her by telling her she's cute or pretty, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.81,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To think someone would try to rip off poor Yuki-chan's clothes and attack her...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.96,0:16:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you poor, poor thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.97,0:16:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, put on Ryota-san's jacket for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.50,0:16:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's guys like you that make women \Nget full of themselves!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.56,0:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.46,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota-san, be careful! \NThat guy's got pro sumo-level strength!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.16,0:17:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a woman!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.73,0:17:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.69,0:17:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.88,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess the secret's out.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.28,0:17:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why? Why would a woman like you do this?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.22,0:17:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As if a beauty like you \Ncould ever understand how I feel!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.40,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was a former sumo wrestler.\NHe made it to the heavyweight division,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.00,0:17:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but he got too fat, blew out his knees, \N and had to retire.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.63,0:17:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I take after him.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.73,0:17:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how little I ate, or even if I only drank water, I just kept getting fatter.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.12,0:18:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I even worried I might gain weight just by breathing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.87,0:18:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,While my friends grew prettier,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.15,0:18:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,my father grabbed me and made me train in sumo.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.61,0:18:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Men ignored me, praised the other girls, \Ndanced, got close, and fell in love with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.53,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The loved ones got even more beautiful, \Ndrawing in more men.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.58,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And even when {\i1}I{\i0} fell in love with a boy,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.12,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,those prettier women\N always stole him away.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.17,0:18:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I know no one ever saw me as a real woman.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.97,0:18:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't forgive women who use their beauty to manipulate men and get all vain about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.89,0:18:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to tear\N women like you apart!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.81,0:18:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.27,0:18:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you want?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.30,Top,,0,0,0,,M-Maruko. {maru ko = round/plump girl - a joke in itself}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.53,Top,,0,0,0,,What of it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.96,0:18:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Maruko, come here a sec!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.51,0:18:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come here, damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.71,0:19:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! What are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not there... {? think she moan "yes, good"}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.10,0:19:17.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,What is this gentle movement of the tongue?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.98,0:19:20.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,I-Is this what they call fondling? {https://jisho.org/word/%E6%84%9B%E6%92%AB}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.89,0:19:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh no, I'm starting to feel weird...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.86,0:19:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, my legs are giving out...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is this... sex?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.97,0:19:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So good...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.50,0:19:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth is Ryota-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.60,0:19:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he's doing it \Nwith that woman.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way... Not our Ryota-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.23,0:19:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Vain women like her are a dime a dozen.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.74,0:19:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll waste your life if you spend it \Ntrying to fight them. {lit: facing that kind of women is the ruin of your life}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.66,0:20:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.33,0:20:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you being so kind \Nto someone like me?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.75,0:20:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it. I just don't get it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.15,0:20:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I see you as a woman.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.42,0:20:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever get lonely, come to me anytime.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.07,0:20:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're fine with me, I'll bed you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.92,0:20:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.02,0:20:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.09,0:20:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.10,0:20:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wh-what are you... {??????? can't hear shit}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.50,0:21:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not again, I'm at my limit! {????????? kinda hear "mou dame" so "I can't hold it anymore"}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.63,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, that sumo girl the other day \Nwas something else.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.49,0:21:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what was something else \Nwas what Ryota-san did.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.97,0:21:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He actually did it with her.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.16,0:21:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's got a pretty wide range, after all. {lit: width is spacious - most likely means that ryota is free-minded/has low standards}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.85,0:21:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Time out! No more, please! \NI'm begging you! {?????? nc what's that first word, kanba or something}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.48,0:22:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! You said if I got lonely, \Nyou'd bed me anytime!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.03,0:22:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So come down here!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.91,0:22:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you this would happen. {??? no clue, sometihng about saying something}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.84,0:22:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I understand I said that, \Nbut every day's too much!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.84,0:22:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break. My body can't take it!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.32,0:22:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I just came up with a haiku:
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.96,0:22:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"After pouring kindness on a white elephant,{??? choubutsu could also be "something long"}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.72,0:22:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what follows is the emptiness\N of being loved and possessed."
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.40,0:22:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Too many syllables. {jiamari = hypermeter; excess syllables in haiku, waka, etc}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.93,0:22:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, is it true you can do hypnosis? {mama as in "the hostess/head girl of the host club"}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.11,0:22:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.59,0:22:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But come on, only dumb guys \Nfall for that stuff, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.86,0:22:45.43,Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know. Want me to try it on you?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.78,0:22:48.07,Top,,0,0,0,,I don't know about this crap.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.15,0:22:50.20,Top,,0,0,0,,Confident, aren't you, Ryota-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:50.85,0:22:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll even let you make me your slave.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.15,0:22:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.58,0:22:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.51,0:22:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, here I go.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.95,0:23:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.02,0:23:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyelids are getting heavy.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.49,0:23:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're feeling so relaxed.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.33,0:23:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you'll do whatever I say.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.78,0:23:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.66,0:23:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Ryota-san actually went under?! \NI don't believe it!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.21,0:23:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Even Rolling Ryota crumbles before me.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.15,0:23:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, call me Mistress. {jou-sama - queen/master}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.52,0:23:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.62,0:23:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes, Mistress.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.46,0:23:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taka-chan, has Ryota been by lately?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.75,0:23:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, \Nhe hasn't shown his face in a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.67,0:23:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like he's working or anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.55,0:23:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably off having fun with some girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:47.19,0:23:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, that's exactly the problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.12,0:23:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If he weren't like that, \NI might actually take him seriously.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.89,0:23:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Whoa there! What do you mean \Nby "take him seriously"?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.76,0:23:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.09,0:24:02.08,Top,,0,0,0,,Maya-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.08,0:24:05.51,Top,,0,0,0,,Ryota's been gone for ten days! {anchan - shortening of "big brother"}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.88,0:24:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten days?! That's big news for this town!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.35,0:24:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the bus depot says he's missed work for ten days straight.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.86,0:24:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think he's floating in Tokyo Bay, do you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.44,0:24:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way, Maya-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.46,0:24:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takashi, you made Maya-chan cry. \NNo good, man!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.43,0:24:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:30.70,0:24:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:32.17,0:24:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota's missing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:36.69,0:24:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:38.54,0:24:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's so damn good.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:40.65,0:24:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You definitely know how to use your device. {????????? no clue what's that nanitte, but it's something wonderful}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:44.07,0:24:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, can I?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:45.70,0:24:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:49.09,0:24:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell? \NRight in front of your little sister?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:52.31,0:24:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it. It feels amazing.\N I've never felt like this before.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:56.22,0:24:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met such a magnificent man before, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:59.84,0:25:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You should try him too!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:01.68,0:25:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right... Some other time.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:03.69,0:25:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:04.61,0:25:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sis, don't you think \Nthis is getting a bit out of hand?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:08.87,0:25:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota-san's been off work for ten days straight.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:11.57,0:25:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got him tending the bar at night,
Dialogue: 10,0:25:13.62,0:25:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,massaging your body during the day, \Nand doing God knows what else.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:17.80,0:25:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the hypnosis hasn't worn off, \Nyou're pushing it.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:22.41,0:25:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:25.38,0:25:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:26.62,0:25:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We take him shopping all day today,\N then I let him go.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:35.52,0:25:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's up, sis?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:37.95,0:25:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aki, don't you feel like \Nit'd be a waste to let Ryota-san go?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:41.67,0:25:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? \NYou've had your fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:45.40,0:25:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I heard from a friend?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:48.37,0:25:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota-san's got a whole bunch \Nof groupies behind him.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:52.79,0:25:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If a new girl tries to make a move on him,\N she gets checked before she even knows it.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:58.58,0:26:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they judge she's not fit for him, \Nthose girls move in and take care of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:03.91,0:26:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way. If that's true, we're screwed!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:09.37,0:26:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Aki, look, those jerks across the street!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:13.09,0:26:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The small-time freeloaders \Nwho always drink for free at our place. {chinpira = street thugs, wannabe yakuza (derogative)}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:16.87,0:26:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. This is our chance, Aki! \NLet's sic Ryota on them!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:21.88,0:26:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is our only chance \Nto get back at those bastards.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:26.25,0:26:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota-san, those three guys coming this way\Nare really bad news.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:31.07,0:26:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're after my body.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:33.23,0:26:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the enemy! \NTake them out, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:36.62,0:26:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sis, they're not just small fry, \Nthey're yakuza!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:40.08,0:26:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:41.71,0:26:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the death-defying \NRolling Ryota, remember? {recklessness; daredevilry; daredevil; reckless person}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:47.46,0:26:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sis, I'm staying out of this!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:54.93,0:26:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, big guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:01.15,0:27:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, check it out, he did it! \NHe really did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:04.76,0:27:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:07.50,0:27:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You there!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:09.29,0:27:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:10.99,0:27:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re under arrest for aggravated assault! {???? cant hear shit}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:17.41,0:27:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that's weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:19.79,0:27:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did the boss go, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:23.06,0:27:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think he got sick \Nof this town and left, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:28.98,0:27:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe he found his dream girl \Nand just ran off with her?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:33.19,0:27:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you even consider that! {lit: that kind of thing would never happen}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:35.55,0:27:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Tajima-san, did you find him?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:38.92,0:27:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:43.89,0:27:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't worry too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:48.06,0:27:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably holed up with some woman.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:50.75,0:27:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys only say that 'cause you don't know what Ryota's life's like!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:57.40,0:27:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets prank calls all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:59.53,0:28:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,People threaten to kill him, saying, "You'll see soon enough."
Dialogue: 10,0:28:02.86,0:28:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Threat letters, challenge notes,\N stacks of them!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:05.54,0:28:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Windows broken in the middle of the night! {??? this sasshi is probably "sash; sliding window frame (esp. metal)" then she says "sash gets broken"}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:07.85,0:28:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time, five guys pretending to be deliverymen barged in with steel pipes!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:13.27,0:28:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota said it himself.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:14.99,0:28:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"These days, all the punks \NI took down are crawling back.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:18.82,0:28:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One life ain't enough anymore."
Dialogue: 10,0:28:21.43,0:28:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I found him! \NThe TV! Turn it up! He's on TV!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:28.94,0:28:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, for real!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:30.77,0:28:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was walking past the electronics store, \Nsaw the crowd gathering, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:35.09,0:28:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Turns out Ryota's been \Nacting as an extra in a TV drama!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:39.70,0:28:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! Look at him beating up the cops!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:43.12,0:28:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. That's the lead role, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:45.93,0:28:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's killing it! \NThat's Ryota for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:48.27,0:28:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots! Look closer!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:49.81,0:28:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a show. He's actually fighting the cops right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:54.80,0:28:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we now bring you a live broadcast.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:57.24,0:29:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The man has already taken down three gangsters and fourteen officers.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:01.45,0:29:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What unbelievable ferocity! Oh, another officer's down!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:05.39,0:29:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nicely done!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:07.14,0:29:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maya-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:08.45,0:29:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell! \NWhy's Boss fighting the cops? {????? nc what's that first part}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:11.98,0:29:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:14.50,0:29:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt he's headed \Nstraight for prison after this!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:17.26,0:29:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For five years at least! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:18.70,0:29:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! The detectives with wooden swords\Nare closing in on the suspect!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:21.89,0:29:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The police have finally decided to use force!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:24.26,0:29:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This has been Takemoto, reporting live! {???? can't hear his name}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:34.63,0:29:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do we do, sis?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:37.55,0:29:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, that's what!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:40.53,0:29:45.67,Top,,0,0,0,,Chief, the guy may be unarmed, \Nbut he's just as dangerous as if he were! {oyaji-san - just someone who's older and more experienced}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:45.67,0:29:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll go.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:48.66,0:29:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, it's too risky to go alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:52.69,0:29:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Komiya, watch closely. {funny how if my hearing serves, this guy is voiced by 若本 規夫 / Wakamoto Norio, who'd actually voice Detective Komiya himself in next year's Ore no Sora OVA; although this episode's credits only list him as Sanji for some reason}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:55.68,0:29:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're about to see my thirty years of experience. {lit: my 30 years career}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:58.28,0:29:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:06.87,0:30:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, punk. \NThat's about enough, I'd say.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:10.33,0:30:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kitajima from the Western Police Station. \NLet's talk this out. {? idk maybe this Nishijou is actually just a place name}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:16.96,0:30:20.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,D-Damn it, I hesitated in front of my underling.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:20.64,0:30:23.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,D-Did he notice?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:25.64,0:30:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! N-Not another step! {????????????? not a word}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:28.12,0:30:32.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ugh! I offered to talk it out, \Nbut my finger's already on the trigger.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:32.26,0:30:35.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,What a gutless fool I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:35.43,0:30:38.48,Thought,,0,0,0,,Right, warning shot. \NI'll stop him with that.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:42.78,0:30:45.20,Thought,,0,0,0,,N-No good. It's not working on him!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:47.45,0:30:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop right there! \NOne more step and I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:54.92,0:30:56.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,Isn't this guy afraid of guns at all?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:56.93,0:31:02.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,If he keeps this up, I'm done for. \NSo this is how my fifty-five years end? {lit: 55 years life}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:02.65,0:31:06.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,That man took down more than\N twenty trained officers barehanded. {nc what's abura here}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:06.44,0:31:08.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,If I take one punch in the face from him...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:08.88,0:31:10.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ah, here he comes!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:11.56,0:31:14.48,Thought,,0,0,0,,He'll shatter the new dentures \NI just had replaced. {post crown; dowel crown; false tooth}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:17.19,0:31:19.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,While I'm wasting time thinking, \Nhe's already this close!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:19.82,0:31:21.48,Thought,,0,0,0,,D-Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:21.48,0:31:26.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,If I miss at this range, the whole precinct \Nwill laugh me out of town. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:26.40,0:31:28.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,The pressure's unbearable. {dunno what to make of this omawaru, probably "of those around me"}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:34.84,0:31:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt... {?????? he says nanika kiita which is either "I heard something" or "something worked/had effect" which I have no idea what to make of}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:41.63,0:31:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That was the bullet \NI fired into the air earlier!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:46.05,0:31:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a miracle! \NA miracle just happened!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:49.21,0:31:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, you did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:51.21,0:31:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,O great gods, have mercy!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:56.27,0:32:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If Ryota-san gets arrested, doesn't that mean \Nthey'll be coming for us too?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:00.67,0:32:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax. If we just play dumb, \Nno one'll ever know.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:05.24,0:32:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! S-Sis, look! \NThe front of our apartment building!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:10.96,0:32:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way. Are those Ryota-san's groupies?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:14.50,0:32:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:16.23,0:32:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Your older sister just peed herself a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:23.17,0:32:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth is he doing in there, \NDetective Kitajima?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:27.51,0:32:31.24,Top,,0,0,0,,Looks like some kind of massage to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:31.89,0:32:34.28,Top,,0,0,0,,Kitajima, look! \NHis movements just changed!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:34.91,0:32:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he trying to do now?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:37.19,0:32:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:46.03,0:32:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That hip motion!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:48.68,0:32:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Classic back position technique! {??? dunno what he's talking about if they only figure out it's sex two lines later, maybe some kind of martial art}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:50.51,0:32:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Amazing hip work!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:53.41,0:32:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I think those are, uh, \Nmovements used during sex.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:57.52,0:32:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:58.80,0:33:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from this, the man's clearly \Nnot of sound mind, Chief.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:04.02,0:33:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he must undergo \Na psychiatric evaluation at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:08.34,0:33:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! Emergency!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:10.82,0:33:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Komiya?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:12.78,0:33:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman who controlled that man \Njust turned herself in!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:16.27,0:33:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:21.96,0:33:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hypnosis?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:24.27,0:33:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hypnosis.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:26.68,0:33:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying he beat up dozens of officers \Nnot of his own will, but under hypnosis?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:34.66,0:33:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:35.85,0:33:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, start from the beginning \Nand explain yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:39.87,0:33:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. At first, it was just a joke. \NI didn't think it'd work so well,
Dialogue: 10,0:33:44.29,0:33:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but he went under deep \Nand did whatever I told him.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:48.22,0:33:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had him bartend at my place, \Nshaking cocktails and all.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:53.97,0:33:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Cocktail shaker?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:55.60,0:33:56.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:56.74,0:34:00.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,So that motion was from \Nshaking a cocktail. Then what?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:00.89,0:34:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I got tired, \NI'd have him give me a little massage.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:06.81,0:34:08.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:08.23,0:34:11.34,Thought,,0,0,0,,So it really was a massage.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:11.34,0:34:14.72,Thought,,0,0,0,,Then those hip movements must've been...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:15.57,0:34:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It became so convenient for me \Nthat I didn't want it to wear off,
Dialogue: 10,0:34:19.10,0:34:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so I reinforced the hypnosis again and again, \Nand now it won't break at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:23.46,0:34:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That went on for about ten days, until today...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:27.67,0:34:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bullshit me! {???? probably very rough-sounding "fuzakeruna"}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:31.44,0:34:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten days of that? \NYou want me to believe that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:35.03,0:34:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That he did nothing but shaking cocktails \Nand giving you massages?!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:38.62,0:34:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to hide something that clumsily \Nwill only make your punishment worse!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:41.89,0:34:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not hiding anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:45.06,0:34:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, nothing?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:58.37,0:35:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You were fucking with that man \Nevery night, weren't you? {borrowed word}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:02.83,0:35:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,From the back too. Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:08.34,0:35:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,From the back... So good...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:12.93,0:35:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:14.82,0:35:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Never underestimate the police.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:17.18,0:35:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, tell us everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:20.06,0:35:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of that, \Nwas the man well-endowed? {????? no clue what's that sukina taiin}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:27.75,0:35:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:29.79,0:35:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are the best interrogator \Nin the Western Station. I learned a lot today.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:34.34,0:35:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with a self-surrendered suspect, \Nyou still go straight for the jugular.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:38.32,0:35:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, she told you everything,\Nfrom her first guy to what turns her on most. {??? assuming this shimai to be "in the end" and otoko henreki to be "history of her men"}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:45.50,0:35:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's what I call a pro.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:48.26,0:35:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly glamorous, Komiya.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:52.43,0:35:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes we have to enjoy our work this way, \Nor we'd never last in this job.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:58.46,0:36:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if that guy really was hypnotized, \Nwhat happens to his charges?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:04.81,0:36:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll depend on the psych evaluation.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:08.58,0:36:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Could he be acquitted in the end?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:11.61,0:36:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:17.88,0:36:19.78,Top,,0,0,0,,Serves him right!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:20.24,0:36:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota's gonna rot in the slammer!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:24.20,0:36:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If they hang him, I'll laugh my head off!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:28.37,0:36:33.46,Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsuki. Celebrate if you want, but cover your mouth when you wrap sushi, will ya? {????? no clue what he means by "run from sushi"}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:33.46,0:36:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're spitting everywhere. Disgusting.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:35.80,0:36:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:37.84,0:36:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the long faces, you two?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:40.61,0:36:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota got busted!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:42.35,0:36:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, just be honest\N about how you feel.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:48.57,0:36:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it! That smile!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:50.83,0:36:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, big discount today!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:53.69,0:36:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling generous, \Nso you get point-one percent off! {no clue what's that omaki, assuming omake = discount; also reitei ichiwaru = 0.1% (one tenth of a percent)}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:56.59,0:36:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:57.59,0:36:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:58.76,0:37:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsuki, you said these were on the house!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:02.29,0:37:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You let us eat all that \Nexpensive stuff and now this?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:07.62,0:37:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the sliced ginger is free for you! {sliced ginger prepared in vinegar (served with sushi); pickled ginger​}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:10.75,0:37:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch, cheapskate.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:13.15,0:37:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tea for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:15.24,0:37:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, why'd Ryota snap all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:19.16,0:37:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not dumb enough to take on the cops.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:22.87,0:37:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know how he is.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:24.67,0:37:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't changed a bit since back then. \NHe's still Nuthead Ryota! {????????? ebisen can only be "ebisenbei; shrimp-flavored rice cracker​" and I have no clue how that can characterize ryota}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:30.42,0:37:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he starts running...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:31.83,0:37:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...he doesn't stop.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:32.76,0:37:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he starts rampaging...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:34.15,0:37:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...he doesn't stop.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:35.61,0:37:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling ya, he's still the same old simple-minded fool he was in school!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:42.66,0:37:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be in pretty high spirits \Nwith Ryota gone, Natsuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:48.29,0:37:51.21,Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, Iwata, is that you? Figures.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:51.70,0:37:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Iwata, \Ndon't look so gloomy!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:55.16,0:37:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Ryota's been arrested!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:01.13,0:38:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Iwata just smiled!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:03.11,0:38:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I've ever \Nseen you smile like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:06.08,0:38:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,True! {????????? no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:08.20,0:38:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, let's start with beer, \Nsea urchin, and salmon roe.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:11.71,0:38:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe throw in a sashimi platter too.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:14.32,0:38:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, Natsuki's treating today.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:16.79,0:38:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that's free is the sliced ginger.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:19.26,0:38:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then make it one cucumber sushi roll for me. {cucumber sushi wrapped in nori; cucumber makizushi}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:25.12,0:38:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Hikita Tonko of the {Great }Japan Hypnosis Federation is going to lift his hypnosis spell.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:31.08,0:38:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the time has finally come.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:33.58,0:38:36.27,Top,,0,0,0,,Now, you will awaken.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:36.27,0:38:39.00,Top,,0,0,0,,When I clap my hands, you will wake up.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:39.34,0:38:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three. Now!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:46.18,0:38:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where am I?!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:47.99,0:38:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, it's finally broken.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:50.54,0:38:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've never had a hypnosis spell\N take a full day to undo before.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:54.51,0:38:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, what's your assessment?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:57.73,0:39:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from the results of various psychiatric tests,
Dialogue: 10,0:39:00.92,0:39:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't say this man \Nis mentally competent.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:04.45,0:39:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's mentally incompetent?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:06.89,0:39:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,After causing such a mess? Damn it.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:10.35,0:39:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't anyone partying at my place?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:13.06,0:39:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your joint's too pricey, that's why.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:16.17,0:39:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just run a tab and have a party!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:18.27,0:39:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, just knowing Ryota's not around \Nkind of makes my heart feel light!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:24.07,0:39:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone, \Nlet's express this feeling loud and clear!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:28.56,0:39:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Skip, skip, run-run-run! {skip in japanese means "hop"}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:30.59,0:39:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Skip, skip, run-run-run!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:32.47,0:39:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Skip, skip, run-run-run!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:36.69,0:39:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That haircut... No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:38.43,0:39:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:39.00,0:39:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:39.89,0:39:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:45.58,0:39:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:47.99,0:39:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn confusing haircut!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:50.41,0:39:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:51.87,0:39:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's okay to walk around \Nwith a haircut like that in our town, huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:55.96,0:39:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Scalp him, dammit! {???????? I think I hear "mawase" but no clue what to make of it}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:57.35,0:39:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:58.46,0:39:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:58.86,0:40:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I see you wandering around\N with that haircut, I'll kill you! Got that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:05.22,0:40:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get lost, you cheap Ryota imitation!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:08.60,0:40:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:12.60,0:40:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You motherfucker!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:14.49,0:40:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Still hanging around here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:18.25,0:40:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You just never learn, do you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:21.84,0:40:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looking at that haircut pisses me off!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:24.44,0:40:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:25.74,0:40:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:40:27.41,0:40:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that again? \NMy haircut pisses you off? {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:30.72,0:40:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not it, Ryota-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:33.28,0:40:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a deeper reason for this{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 10,0:40:35.30,0:40:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:40:39.80,0:40:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Komiya. He's done it again. \NCaught red-handed.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:43.50,0:40:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Let's arrest him.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:45.86,0:40:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,At least now the colleagues \Nhe hurt will get some justice.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:49.21,0:40:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:50.12,0:40:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:52.22,0:40:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chief?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:53.76,0:40:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That man, Takao Ryota...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:56.12,0:40:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he'd be more useful \Nswimming free than locked in a cell.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:59.94,0:41:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why's that, sir?!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:02.78,0:41:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look closely at the men he just beat down.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:06.86,0:41:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsuki, the crooked sushi chef,\Nwho lights the charcoal grill just to vent his rage
Dialogue: 10,0:41:10.76,0:41:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and doesn't hesitate to swing\N his kitchen knife in the streets. {?????????????????? this whole first half is like ???}
Dialogue: 10,0:41:14.95,0:41:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kariya and Nemuro, the hotheaded pachinko clerks who lash out at the slightest thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:21.34,0:41:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwata, whose sense of direction's so bad \Nhe spends more time in jail than out. {?????????}
Dialogue: 10,0:41:25.30,0:41:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Our town's crawling with that sort.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:29.32,0:41:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,An electric eel will sometimes \Nsnap at a fisherman,
Dialogue: 10,0:41:33.14,0:41:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but other times, it stuns a whole school of fish \Nand makes the fisherman happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:38.06,0:41:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to earn a pension \Nthan get hurt for nothing, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:41.96,0:41:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right, Chief.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:44.59,0:41:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The world really does have its balance. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:48.03,0:41:50.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:50.25,0:41:52.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,But maybe this is how things are meant to be.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.52,0:20:36.72,Song,,0,0,0,,My job {地球の隅で歌をうたおう by 	\N春日章一郎; going by ear, copying from episode 1}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.39,0:20:44.73,Song,,0,0,0,,Is to do justice
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.35,0:20:52.57,Song,,0,0,0,,To sing songs
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.64,0:21:01.34,Song,,0,0,0,,In the far corners of the Earth
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.46,0:21:09.94,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll stay free
Dialogue: 5,0:21:12.25,0:21:17.93,Song,,0,0,0,,Until I die
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.57,0:21:27.65,Song,,0,0,0,,In this corner of the Earth
Dialogue: 5,0:21:28.87,0:21:38.42,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll sing my songs
Dialogue: 10,0:42:05.41,0:42:11.35,Song,,0,0,0,,Someone trusted me with their life {"Korogashi Ryouta no Uta"; going by ear, copying from episode 1}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:11.35,0:42:16.82,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll give them mine
Dialogue: 10,0:42:16.82,0:42:19.78,Song,,0,0,0,,In the rear view, the city shines
Dialogue: 10,0:42:19.78,0:42:23.24,Song,,0,0,0,,With the eyes of starving beasts
Dialogue: 10,0:42:23.24,0:42:33.40,Song,,0,0,0,,Ambitious guys, they don't care for your opinion
Dialogue: 10,0:42:33.40,0:42:45.16,Song,,0,0,0,,That's how I roll, roll, roll, roll, Rolling Ryota
